+   50 fully-symbolic bytes that explode the lexer/parser. Remedy: on the
+   FIRST SRC_FILE read (get_src_buf below), fork ONCE on a symbolic
+   klee_range selector, pick a concrete entry from this menu of complete,
+   valid awk programs, klee_assume the symbolic buffer equals that entry (so
+   the emitted ktest replays the exact program on the native gawk coverage
